        <h2>Component Packages</h2>
        <p>Tail.Blazor is organized into 12 modular NuGet packages:</p>
        
        <h3>Core Packages</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Tail.Blazor.Core</strong> - Base components, theme engine, and core functionality</li>
            <li><strong>Tail.Blazor.Utils</strong> - JavaScript interop helpers and utilities</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>UI Component Packages</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Tail.Blazor.Buttons</strong> - Button components (Button, IconButton, FAB, Toggle, Split, Group)</li>
            <li><strong>Tail.Blazor.Forms</strong> - Form components (Input, Select, Checkbox, DatePicker, FileUpload, etc.)</li>
            <li><strong>Tail.Blazor.Layout</strong> - Layout components (Card, Panel, Grid, Container, Divider)</li>
            <li><strong>Tail.Blazor.Navigation</strong> - Navigation components (Sidebar, Menu, Tabs, Accordion, Carousel, Steps)</li>
            <li><strong>Tail.Blazor.Feedback</strong> - Feedback components (Alert, Badge, Dialog, Toast, Progress, Spinner)</li>
            <li><strong>Tail.Blazor.Icons</strong> - Icon components with Heroicons, Lucide, and custom SVG support</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Data & Visualization Packages</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Tail.Blazor.Data</strong> - Data components (DataGrid, Scheduler, Tree, PivotDataGrid, ListView, Pager)</li>
            <li><strong>Tail.Blazor.Charts</strong> - Chart components (Chart, Sparkline) with SVG/Canvas rendering</li>
            <li><strong>Tail.Blazor.Visualization</strong> - Visualization components (ArcGauge, QRCode, Timeline)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Validation Package</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Tail.Blazor.Validators</strong> - Validation components (Required, Email, Regex, Length, Custom, NumericRange, Compare)</li>
        </ul>

